{"tid":1898090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不了電話 不了旅行嗰啲","createTime":"2020-02-26T03:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T02:59:08.000Z","uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"937abb6a167403a49ee820af0f3165ce87059cb6","tid":1898090,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下會買咩電話同去邊到旅行？<br />\n<br />\n仆你個臭街，啲網軍煩撚到，係咁失敗主義，話睇唔起香港人會捐錢<br />\n<br />\n宜家仲邊有人出街買野？機場都無咗98%嘅客，你同我講你收到10,000會去旅行，去邊撚到咁撚把炮呀？日本呀？睇奧運呀？韓國呀？大丘呀？<br />\n<br />\n失敗主義收撚皮啦！乜都不了不了你唔撚死柒咗佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLZ2Pcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLZ2Pcc.jpg&h=68fa04cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6VUFiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6VUFiS.jpg&h=84126936&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGovdDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGovdDT.jpg&h=21efaa18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucSG4Lz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucSG4Lz.jpg&h=58f304f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5sjRqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5sjRqz.jpg&h=bdf1bf78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5FC70iV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5FC70iV.jpg&h=2a75a46e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwHWTDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwHWTDW.jpg&h=a296b639&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZTVERqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZTVERqC.jpg&h=e0c3f695&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDk5MYX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDk5MYX.jpg&h=bbd6c0af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRc0ASi.jpg\" data-thumbn